Yet Another PHP Shell - tiny and smart!

To generate new password, type in console:

$ php -r "echo hash('sha256','myPassword');"

Open yaphpsh.php, copy result of this command to string with
$password = 'PASTE HERE';

Done!

Features:
* SHA-256 hashing.
* Generates a salt for every command; it expires after 15 seconds.
* Not use session or cookies.
* Not use any external libraries except clear php and javascript.
* Do not reloads a page.
* Handles path changes made by 'cd'.
* Supports command history (beta).
* One file with size just 6,21 KB!
